      <abstract>
        <label>Abstract</label>
        <p>A new <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Episcaphium</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> species collected from Yunnan Province of China is described as <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Episcaphium</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">zhuxiaoyui</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> <bold>sp. n.</bold>, and its diagnostic characters are illustrated. A new province record of <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Episcaphium</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">haematoides</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> is reported. A key to the <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Episcaphium</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> species recorded from China is provided.</p>
