            <caption>
              <p>
          <bold>11</bold> Living <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Episcaphium</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">zhuxiaoyui</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> sp. n. on fungus <bold>12</bold> Collector Mr. Zhu Xiao-Yu and log with fungus. Photo by Mr. Jian-Qing Zhu.</p>
            </caption>
            <graphic xlink:href="zookeys-595-e8784-g003.jpg" position="float" orientation="portrait" xlink:type="simple" id="oo_90928.jpg"/>
          </fig>
