          <p>
            <bold>China: Gansu</bold>: 1♂, Lazikou Valley, 2020–2510 m, 34°09.9–10.1'N, 103°48.2–51.9'E, 28.VI.2005, J. Hájek, D. Král &amp; J. Růžička leg. (<named-content content-type="dwc:institutional_code">NMPC</named-content>)</p>
        </tp:treatment-sec>
        <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="distribution">
          <title>Distribution.</title>
          <p>This species was previously known from Yunnan and Sichuan. The above male represents the first record from Gansu.</p>
        </tp:treatment-sec>
